description: Redevelopment of the site for 69 residential units comprising a two storey gate house and three storey house and garage facing Stowe Road; Two terraces of 15, three storey houses over basement with rooftop winter gardens and terraces; One terrace of 3, three storey houses over basement; One three storey building comprising 49 flats; provision of 72 car parking spaces (including 5 disabled spaces), cycle parking and associated landscaping.
